{"title":"蜡枪头银样","authors":["池北偶"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":3,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜡枪头银样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“特种”大使，特种排场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出入不离保镖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"官邸十足牢房。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周围密布铁丝网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四面架起机关枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“战略村”也远远赶不上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表面强装镇静，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里实在虚慌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹窗户胆吓破，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂钟报时当枪响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怕的是人民武装来算账。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堂堂南越“太上皇”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却是蜡枪头银样。（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国驻西贡“大使”洛奇住在如此警卫森严、用双重铁丝网保护起来的“大使馆”里。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}